trans-unit.source: Represents an assembly reference and the namespace imported from that assembly.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un riferimento all'assembly e lo spazio dei nomi importato da tale assembly.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> to provide assembly references and namespaces required for expression compilation.
trans-unit.target: Questa classe viene utilizzata da <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> e da <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> per fornire i riferimenti all'assembly e gli spazi dei nomi necessari per la compilazione dell'espressione.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the full name of the assembly referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta il nome completo dell'assembly a cui fa riferimento questo oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The full name of the assembly referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Nome completo dell'assembly a cui fa riferimento questo oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> to compare with the current <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> da confrontare con l'oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> corrente.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Determina se l'oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> specificato è uguale all'oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> corrente.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se l'oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> specificato è uguale all'oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> corrente; in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce il codice hash per l'istanza di <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The hash code for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" /> instance.
Gets or sets the imported namespace referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta lo spazio dei nomi importato a cui fa riferimento questo oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The imported namespace referenced by this <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
trans-unit.target: Spazio dei nomi importato a cui fa riferimento questo oggetto <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicImportReference" />.
